This example demonstrates the usage of <strong>receiveStateFocus</strong>.<br />
<br/>
The first button <strong>always sets</strong> the focus of input next to it to true when clicked.
<br/><br/>
The second button <strong>toggles</strong> the focus of the input when clicked.
<br/><br/>
<i>The input receives a <strong>lightgreen</strong> color when <strong>focused</strong>.</i>